# Cloudflare Pages routing for moavoca.com
#
# Static assets (HTML pages, _expo bundle, etc.) are served from disk
# first by CF Pages — only paths with no matching file fall through to
# these rules. We need a SPA fallback for the Expo Web subpath so
# Expo Router-driven dynamic routes (e.g. /app/wordlist/<uuid>,
# /app/invite/<code>) hand control to the client bundle. Static landing
# at / and the legal docs at /privacy.html etc. are unaffected because
# they exist on disk and resolve before this rule.
#
# IMPORTANT: asset paths (anything under /app/_expo/ or /app/assets/)
# MUST return a real 404 when missing instead of falling back to
# index.html. A stale chunk URL (cached old hash referenced by an
# updated entry bundle) would otherwise return HTML, which the browser
# tries to parse as JavaScript and crashes with "Unexpected token '<'".

/app/_expo/*    /app/_expo/:splat    404
/app/assets/*   /app/assets/:splat   404
/app/*          /app/index.html      200
